videos.headline: 57-yard run sets up LSU TD
videos.description: Clyde Edwards-Helaire goes up the middle for a 57-yard run and on the next play Joe Burrow finds Ja'Marr Chase for a 9-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (57-yard run sets up LSU TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trask connects with Grimes for TD
videos.description: Kyle Trask finds Trevon Grimes in the back of the end zone for a 5-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Trask connects with Grimes for TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jefferson stays in for 7-yard TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow connects with Justin Jefferson for an LSU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Jefferson stays in for 7-yard TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Perine catches TD off deflection
videos.description: Emory Jones' pass is popped up in the air and hauled in by Lamical Perine for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Perine catches TD off deflection) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Edwards-Helaire runs for 39-yard TD
videos.description: Clyde Edwards-Helaire takes the handoff 39 yards for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Edwards-Helaire runs for 39-yard TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trask throws 2nd TD before halftime
videos.description: Kyle Trask connects with Van Jefferson for a six-yard Florida touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Trask throws 2nd TD before halftime) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jefferson helped off field after TD catch
videos.description: Van Jefferson is assisted off the field after holding on for a two-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Jefferson helped off field after TD catch) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Edwards-Helaire powers in for his 2nd TD
videos.description: Clyde Edwards-Helaire goes up the middle for a 5-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Edwards-Helaire powers in for his 2nd TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Davis-Price blows past Florida defense for 33-yard TD
videos.description: Tyrion Davis-Price breaks through the hole and runs in to give LSU the lead.

videos.headline: Stingley picks Trask in red zone
videos.description: Kyle Trask throws to the end zone and is intercepted by Derek Stingley Jr.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Stingley picks Trask in red zone) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow connects with Chase for 54-yard TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow throws to Ja'Marr Chase, who takes off for a 54-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Burrow connects with Chase for 54-yard TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: LSU stonewalls Florida to secure victory
videos.description: Kyle Trask runs to the right and is stopped short of the goal line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (LSU stonewalls Florida to secure victory) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Orgeron: LSU's defense made plays when they had to
videos.description: Ed Orgeron says the LSU defensive strategy changed in the second half as they pulled away to beat Florida.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Orgeron: LSU's defense made plays when they had to) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow makes the Heisman chase look easy
videos.description: LSU QB Joe Burrow is interested in time travel, and his efficient game against Florida makes it seem like he might have mastered it.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Burrow makes the Heisman chase look easy) 2019/10/12 ESHEET ENHL
